    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LogiKing 是...</h2><strong>...加冕逻辑之王的游戏！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262240/extras/9a0e46035a29af865676f10998440db7.poster.avif?t=1768443799\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262240/extras/9a0e46035a29af865676f10998440db7.webm?t=1768443799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262240/extras/9a0e46035a29af865676f10998440db7.mp4?t=1768443799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>LogiKing 是一款游戏，您可以利用编号为 0 到 9 的 10 张卡牌的效果来推断对手的隐藏卡牌！<br>规则很简单，但有深度，可以让您对对手进行战略和战术思考。登上王位，成为逻辑之王！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >史诗般的战斗</h2><strong>最大的兴奋！</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262240/extras/e02ce1938de6c95d5b2e5129500d1182.poster.avif?t=1768443799\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262240/extras/e02ce1938de6c95d5b2e5129500d1182.webm?t=1768443799\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262240/extras/e02ce1938de6c95d5b2e5129500d1182.mp4?t=1768443799\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>无论您是游戏新手还是经验丰富的老手，LogiKing 都有令人兴奋的视觉和声音供大家享受！<br>当您正确猜出他们的隐藏数字之一时，体验迫使对手进入“逻辑”的快感！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在线全球配对</h2><strong>随时随地玩</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262240/extras/5cc50f51130f874b1394e0d72aab7e02.avif?t=1768443799\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>实时挑战世界各地的其他人。与朋友、家人和神秘的强大敌人一起玩 LogiKing 吧！",
